<p>I'll clear out the require lines entirely so we can really enjoy things.
But now the burning question is: did I break anything? Go back and run <code>gulp</code>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">gulp</div></code></pre>
<p>Hey, no errors! So if this shorter syntax feels cool to you, go for it.
If you hate the magic, no big deal - keep those requires.</p>

    
